OL,3,CLA tech trial must be turning point `
OL,4,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex's
OL,5,Cspokesperson
OL,7,FThe LA trial over whether social media
OL,8,Fcompanies should be liable for harms
OL,9,Fcaused to children using their
OL,10,Fplatforms is a "turning point" and the
OL,11,F"world is finally paying attention", a
OL,12,Fspokesperson for the Duke and Duchess
OL,13,Fof Sussex said.
OL,15,FIt comes after Harry and Meghan called
OL,16,Ffor stronger protections for children
OL,17,Fonline last year after unveiling a
OL,18,Fmemorial in New York City to young
OL,19,Fpeople who lost their lives due to the
OL,20,Fharmful effects of social media.
OL,26,@rD@POUrD@^O]sD@AOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
