OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773720212
OL,3,CLA tech trial must be turning point `
OL,4,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex's
OL,5,Cspokesperson
OL,7,FAnd the Sussexes' Archewell Foundation
OL,8,Fpreviously unveiled its Parents'
OL,9,FNetwork initiative as a support system
OL,10,Ffor parents of children affected by
OL,11,Fonline harm.
OL,13,FNow closing arguments have been heard
OL,14,Fat the Spring Street Courthouse in Los
OL,15,FAngeles after about a month of hearing
OL,16,Ffrom therapists, addiction experts,
OL,17,Fplatform engineers and executives,
OL,18,Fincluding Mark Zuckerberg in the trial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
