OL,3,CLA tech trial must be turning point `
OL,4,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex's
OL,5,Cspokesperson
OL,7,FThe plaintiff is a 20-year-old woman
OL,8,Fand the two defendants are Meta and
OL,9,FGoogle-owned YouTube. Snap and TikTok
OL,10,Fwere also named defendants in the
OL,11,Flawsuit, but each settled before the
OL,12,Ftrial started.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
