PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773720212
OL,3,CLA tech trial must be turning point `
OL,4,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex's
OL,5,Cspokesperson
OL,7,F"Today, the largest technology
OL,8,Fcompanies find themselves under
OL,9,Funprecedented scrutiny. Their
OL,10,Fproducts, their design choices, and
OL,11,Ftheir impact on young people are being
OL,12,Fexamined not just in public debate,
OL,13,Fbut now in a court of law. And
OL,14,Fregardless of any single verdict, one
OL,15,Ftruth is already clear: these
OL,16,Fcompanies are on trial in the court of
OL,17,Fhistory. This is the first case of its
OL,18,Fkind, but it will not be the last.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773720212
OL,3,CLA tech trial must be turning point `
OL,4,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex's
OL,5,Cspokesperson
OL,7,F"For years, these companies resisted
OL,8,Ftransparency and pointed to a supposed
OL,9,Flack of 'definitive proof' whenever
OL,10,Fpeople raised alarms about harm. When
OL,11,Fwhistleblowers raised alarms about
OL,12,Finternal practices, Meta leadership
OL,13,Fsaid the claims were 'misleading' and
OL,14,Ftaken out of context. But the
OL,15,Fdisclosures in this case have set the
OL,16,Frecord straight.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773720212
OL,3,CLA tech trial must be turning point `
OL,4,CDuke and Duchess of Sussex's
OL,5,Cspokesperson
OL,7,F"Internal emails, strategy decks, and
OL,8,Fresearch`documents the public was
OL,9,Fnever meant to see`are now evidence.
OL,10,FThey reveal not only what these
OL,11,Fcompanies built, but what they knew."
OL,13,FThey added: "This trial is already a
OL,14,Fturning point: it has forced some of
OL,15,Fthe most powerful companies on earth
OL,16,Fto reveal what's behind the curtain
OL,17,Fand to answer, in public and on the
OL,18,Frecord, for choices that shaped an
OL,19,Fentire generation's daily life."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@eO]uD@MOU{D@`O]
